data.title: King Faisal the Second, 1952
data.meta_description: 13 images. King Faisal the Second, 30 August 1952. Prince Abdul-Ilah (Regent of Iraq)King Faisal the Second of Iraq.Caption slip reads: "Photographer: Paegel. Date: 08-30. Reporter: Parker. Assignment: King Faisal II at Ambassador. King Faisal II, boy monarch of Iraq, stops by Ambassador Hotel pool before heading for tour of MGM Studio. L to R: Prince Abdul-Ilah, regent of Iraq until King Faisal at right, becomes 18 next year.
